  "text": "Foaming of whey protein concentrate is affected by solubility and the amount of residual lipid in the product [CITATION_1] . By filtering the whey protein concentrate slurry to remove large molecular mass components, [CITATION_2] improved the foaming property of whey protein concentrate samples. We have also observed that removing large particles by sieving redistributes the amount of fat present in the WPC80 products improved foam volume, particularly in the smallest particle size fractions (Table 3) .",
